# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Drishti monorepo — root .gitignore
# (each app folder also has its own .gitignore; those still apply)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Local backups of the old per-app git repos (kept for reference, NOT tracked).
# The corresponding GitHub repos remain intact; this is just a local safety copy.
.git-backups-old-repos/

# Dependencies & build output (belt-and-suspenders; app .gitignores also cover these)
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/
**/dist/

# Secrets — never track real env files (but DO keep .env.example templates)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env*.local

# Logs & misc
**/*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
